        <mxCell id="YHspKHzTNkOGivLqeAL_-18" value="The Simulation Handler would need to calculate&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;how many simulations are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;necessary and call on&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;the testbench&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;to generate and regenerate the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;exported_tags file that many times&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="620" y="525" width="280" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="YHspKHzTNkOGivLqeAL_-19" value="How to combine that with the RandomTagGenerator?&lt;div&gt;using the TagGenerator as an oracle we do not know if and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;what timesteps can be ignored in the simulations&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(the point of random was also to reduce number of simulations!)&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1" vertex="1">
